*   ## **_BRYAN DANIELSON DEF. NIGEL MCGUINNESS_**
    

Nigel mouths THANK YOU to Bryan as he taps. Nigel McGuinness has been given his catharsis. He has finally had his moment on national TV with Bryan Danielson.

Christian Cage runs out to cash in on Bryan. Kip Sabian won't allow it. Christian chases Kip off and runs into PAC and CLAUDIO who appeared to be waiting to jump Bryan backstage.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/78f23028-76db-4f45-988e-9eccc651aaba/Screenshot_20240925_172957.jpg)

