HOOK has officially retired the FTW Championship in an emotional moment with his father TAZ

This is NYC where the title was created way back in ECW.

## **_HOOK DEF. RODERICK STRONG_** in the very last FTW Championship defense. Roderick shook Hooks hand and shows respect after the match was done.

